					<Text>Section 17 has been amended by the Police and Justice Act 2006; the Policing and Crime Act <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2009/26" id="c00007" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct" Year="2009" Number="0026">2009 (c. 26)</Citation>; the Local Democracy, Economic Development and Construction Act <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2009/20" id="c00008" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct" Year="2009" Number="0020">2009 (c. 20)</Citation>; the Policing and Crime Act <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2017/3" id="c00009" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct" Year="2017" Number="0003">2017 (c. 3)</Citation>; the Police Reform and Social Responsibility Act <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2011/13" id="c00010" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct" Year="2011" Number="0013">2011 (c. 13)</Citation>; <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2008/78" id="c00011" Class="UnitedKingdomStatutoryInstrument" Year="2008" Number="0078">S.I. 2008/78</Citation>; and the Localism Act <Citation URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2011/20" id="c00012" Class="UnitedKingdomPublicGeneralAct" Year="2011" Number="0020">2011 (c. 20)</Citation>. There are other amendments but they are not relevant to this Order.</Text>
